==== Strategy ====
'''Do Not Attack:'''
* Angels
* Renegade Bases
* Scaven Forts / Watchtowers (until Withdraw is trained)

'''Step-by-step:'''
# Do not attack anything — find an Outpost first
# In Firewells, activate them for potential Outpost coordinates
# At the Outpost, do Tag Droid missions 4× to get 12 Mercreds; hire a '''Praetor'''
# Do Cave Crystal missions; attack Tag Droids and cave enemies only
# At 10 Mercreds, hire a '''Centurion'''; at 12 Mercreds, hire an '''Orbie'''
# Take the Matriarch Mission; find a Scaven Settlement; get Scaven mercs
