'''Cash farming tips:'''
* Sell Stun Lasers for 900 cash each
* Enter Plateaus after doing Azra for additional Tag Droids
* With Greed active, Tag Droids and Azra are the primary cash sources

==== End of Patrol 1 ====
Leave patrol when you have ~47 spare Mercreds and ~485k–500k cash.

