== Progression Variations ==

Different Controllers approach Vulcore differently. Here are the main strategic variations:

=== Standard (Fallen meta — this guide) ===
{{MessageBox
| header = Outdated meta notice
| text   = This variation uses the [[Fallen]] for [[Greed]] and [[Dark Union]]. A newer Angels-based meta may be more efficient — see the notice at the top of this page.
}}
The most well-documented approach. Focuses on:
* Dual Baron Laser Valadin start
* Banking missions to 12 Mercreds; retreat from Tag Trackers if enemy has a Reaper
* Hire Praetor, Cave Crystal missions, hire Centurion and Orbie
* 4 Crowns from Sun Ritual — no need to farm excess Mercreds before Scaven
* Get Scaven mercs, train Withdraw, level Valadin almost to 6, get −25 alignment for Greed
* Leave Scaven; Greed run to 500k cash; focus on Tag Droids and Azra only
* Take Plateau after 400k cash for more Tag Droids

=== Double Fallen runs ===
A highly optimised approach focused on safety:
* Standard dual Baron Laser Valadin start; single Argon Laser, CCU training to Level 1, sell Argon
* Banking missions to 12 Mercreds; retreat from Tag Trackers if enemy has a Reaper
* Hire Praetor, Cave Crystal missions, hire Centurion and Orbie
* 4 Crowns from Sun Ritual — no excess Mercred farming needed before Scaven
* Get Scaven mercs, train Withdraw, level Valadin almost to 6, get −25 alignment for Greed
* Leave Scaven; Greed run to 500k cash; focus on Tag Droids and Azra only
* Take Plateau after 400k cash for more Tag Droids
* Workshop upgrade; buy 3 Reapers with EM Syphon; Valadin to MR100s
* '''Set Reaper targeting to Most Reactor — very important; much safer to click Continue instead of manual targeting'''
* Patrol 2: Hire Zodiac, Copius, Orbie; get Scaven mercs; train Withdraw; level Reapers almost to AI 7; get ~28 Crowns; get all negative alignment possible; leave Scaven; Greed to 1.2M cash; return Crowns and buy Storm Shield before leaving patrol
* Patrol 3: Two workshop upgrades; upgrade Reapers to Pulse Beam and Syphonic Disruptor; buy 2 Seers with Comwave, Storm Shield, Anom, Sec Counter, 2 T-Subs
* Patrol 4: Hire 2 Zodiacs and Adverse; get Fallen; MCs — take Cysent; get Magma segments; go to Sulphur; get Crus Tech; buy 2 Crusaders; spend excess cash on Argon Lasers; level until newest Seers are AI 10; Azra before leaving
* Patrol 5: Hire 2 Zodiacs and Adverse; get Fallen; Sulphur until Cysent/Crus AI 13; buy 10 Mech Obvs, 2 Flux, 2 TC7s; make sure you have Magmatic by end; buy 3 DAX Pods

